[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/weak_2s"]
[Student "S"]
{You have a good Weak 2-Bid but East already opened. So you just make a Weak Jump Overcall of 2\S. West passes and partner raises to 3\S. East passes.  

Pass. Partner is in charge. If he had wanted you to bid again he could have forced you with 2NT.}

